hose pages you specify.\n- If you’d like live, broad search capability, we can set up a free-tier or trial browsing API (requires keys) or you can enable Brave key and I’ll guide you through testing.\n\nTell me which route you prefer:\n1) Provide specific YouTube URLs to fetch and summarize.\n2) Provide target topics/sources and I’ll fetch from those exact pages you list.\n3) Enable a free/bare-bones browsing setup (I’ll guide you through obtaining any free keys and doing initial tests)."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":5282,"output":832,"cacheRead":11648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17762,"cost":{"input":-5282,"output":-832,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-6114}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772324350016}}
