{"type":"message","id":"3efdbcaa","parentId":"dae66cf0","timestamp":"2026-03-01T00:49:13.798Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering memory requirements**\n\nI need to acknowledge the memory requirement and plan to save a memory entry. I’ll note down the user's preferences, like sending a daily digest to their work email at 08:30, including high-level details with a drilldown and a markdown attachment. I can ask if they want to confirm this later. I’ll go ahead and set a persistent note in MEMORY.md under the Austin profile and ask for confirmation to proceed with the live preview email.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it. I’ll remember:\n\n- Daily OpenCopilot digest sent to austin.king@parallon.com\n- Time: 08:30 local\n- Content: high-level digest with drill-down attachment in Markdown\n- Attachments: Markdown drill-down report included\n- Stored config: copilot-pro.json and daily_report scripts set up\n\nWould you like me to run a test preview now and email you a sample, or wait for the scheduled live digest at 08:30?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":21981,"output":397,"cacheRead":13696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36074,"cost":{"input":-21981,"output":-397,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-22378}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772326148423}}
