{"type":"message","id":"cf0c5c24","parentId":"19720848","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:30:47.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Updating policy and configuration**\n\nI need to respond by outlining the update procedure for our policy and config steps. The plan is to route Tier 1 and 2 to free providers initially, with OpenRouter as the spillover. I'll update the ROUTING_POLICY.md and COPILOT config to reflect this, making sure to maintain sensitive information. I should ask if any auth keys are stored before proceeding. The user asked to continue, referring to the provider names they provided, so I'll move forward with the changes. Let’s get writing!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_qGZ6tBLS6khvpXyUWH6EryLm","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace/config/copilot-pro.json","content":"{\n  \"email\": \"austin.king@parallon.com\",\n  \"report_time\": \"08:30\",\n  \"budget_monthly_usd\": 20.00,\n  \"default_tier\": \"tier-1\",\n  \"routing_rules\": \"deterministic-v1\",\n  \"digest_depth\": \"high-level\",\n  \"attachment_format\": \"markdown\",\n  \"drilldown\": true,\n  \"fallback_provider\": \"free-first\",\n  \"fallback_settings\": {\n    \"providers_order\": [\"google-gemini-pro-3.1-preview\", \"gpt-5.3-codex\"],\n    \"opens_router_spillover\": true\n  }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":39437,"output":511,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41484,"cost":{"input":-39437,"output":-511,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-39948}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772328640578}}
