{"type":"message","id":"30030739","parentId":"4b065baf","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:59:21.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Providing email status update**\n\nI need to give a status update since we can't directly access email. I’ll let the user know we attempted to send the email and to check their spam folder. It might be helpful to confirm their email address, which I recall is austin.king@parallon.com. I’ll mention that we sent a neutral sender test email and suggest they check both the inbox and spam. If it’s not there, we can retry or use an alternative method.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I don’t have live inbox access here, but I just queued the neutral-sender test email. Please check your inbox and spam/junk folder for a message from “OpenCopilot Preview” with the subject “Daily Digest Preview.” If it isn’t there, I can retry with a different path or resend in a few minutes—want me to retry now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":43692,"output":229,"cacheRead":1792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45713,"cost":{"input":-43692,"output":-229,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-43921}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772330356239}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9e9ebbd","parentId":"30030739","timestamp":"2026-03-01T02:00:20.162Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-01 02:00 UTC] [System Message] [sessionId: db7b1612-eaf3-416c-bec6-ae2bdfbb4c45] A cron job \"Austin Improvement Pulse\" just completed successfully.\n\nResult:\n<ctrl46><ctrl46>\n\nStats: runtime 20s • tokens 16.7k (in 8.8k / out 7.9k)\n\nA completed cron job is ready for user delivery. Convert the result above into your normal assistant voice and send that user-facing update now. Keep this internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type), and do not copy the system message verbatim. Reply ONLY: NO_REPLY if this exact result was already delivered to the user in this same turn."}],"timestamp":1772330420155}}
