{"type":"message","id":"292fc4d8","parentId":"6d41bea9","timestamp":"2026-03-01T14:30:17.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Addressing user concerns**\n\nI see the user thinks the emails might be linked to something I'm doing. It's important to acknowledge their point of view and propose actionable steps. I'll suggest pausing email sending, verifying the configuration, or rerouting to a local preview. The steps will include stopping the test emails, confirming the sender, and checking the copilot-pro configuration. I want to keep it concise and empathetic, offering a few options like pausing email sending or proceeding with caution.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Thanks for flagging that. If you think the email retries are coming from me, I can pause outbound mail and reconfigure to only deliver local previews until you approve.\n\nOptions:\n- Pause outbound emails: I can stop sending test/digest emails until you explicitly re-enable.\n- Switch to local previews only: continue generating the digest locally (Markdown) and share here, no email.\n- Use a whitelisted relay: if you provide an approved SMTP relay, I can route through that and avoid the local gateway block.\n\nTell me which you prefer, and I’ll implement it right away."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":53136,"output":382,"cacheRead":1280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54798,"cost":{"input":-53136,"output":-382,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-53518}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772375412058}}
