{"type":"message","id":"fd0f24c4","parentId":"499340f5","timestamp":"2026-03-01T15:56:20.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Thanks for the update. The latest run shows an authentication failure against the iCloud relay (535). A few quick paths to get back on track:\n\nWhat to fix\n- Recreate a fresh app password for the Dougyfresh_bot@icloud.com account (some relays require a new app password after key changes or timeouts).\n- Double‑check the exact ICLOUD_EMAIL and ICLOUD_APP_PASSWORD loaded in the session (they must match the values in your icloud_mail.env).\n- Confirm the recipient you want for the dry-run is valid and whitelisted for that sender (you mentioned the work address is in memory; if you want me to use that, I’ll route the dry-run to austin.king@parallon.com as the test recipient).\n\nRecommended next steps (quick and safe)\n- Step 1: Generate a fresh iCloud App Password for the Dougyfresh_bot@icloud.com account (via Apple ID security page) and update your icloud_mail.env accordingly.\n- Step 2: Reload credentials in the session:\n  - source /home/ec2-user/.openclaw/credentials/icloud_mail.env\n- Step 3: Re-run the health check with dry-run enabled and WORK_EMAIL set to a known-good recipient (e.g., austin.king@parallon.com if that mailbox is reachable via the iCloud relay).\n- Step 4: If the handshake succeeds, you’ll get an OK plus a confirmation about the dry-run delivery status.\n\nWhat I can do for you now\n- I can swap the dry-run recipient to the in-memory work address you want (austin.king@parallon.com) and re-run the test as soon as you confirm the recipient is acceptable for the iCloud relay.\n- I can also set up a safe “dry-run only” mode that never sends to external mail until you explicitly approve the recipient in this session.\n\nWould you like me to update the dry-run recipient to austin.king@parallon.com and attempt the test again, using a freshly generated app password if you can provide it, or should I queue a fresh app-password request on your side?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":57088,"output":630,"cacheRead":23808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81526,"cost":{"input":-57088,"output":-630,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-57718}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772380574851}}
