{"type":"message","id":"d172e6e2","parentId":"92f3360b","timestamp":"2026-03-01T17:27:10.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Diagnosing email issues**\n\nI need to respond since the user's password updated, but the mailbox still shows an error. I should outline some diagnosis steps, like verifying the recipient and ensuring relay access. It might be helpful to try a different recipient and make sure the correct From address is allowed—maybe even whitelist it. I can suggest testing with a handshake-only method and propose setting WORK_EMAIL to a known-good mailbox or skipping dry-run until the recipient is whitelisted. Let’s ask which recipient to try next!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Thanks. The new iCloud App Password loaded, but the SMTP handshake still shows “Mailbox does not exist” for the dry-run recipient.\n\nWhat’s likely going on\n- The Dougyfresh_bot@icloud.com account may be allowed to log in, but the recipient austin.king@parallon.com isn’t reachable via that iCloud relay (or isn’t whitelisted for that sender).\n- Some relays require the exact recipient to be whitelisted for that sender.\n\nWhat I can do next (two solid options)\n- Option 1: Use a known-good recipient for the dry-run\n  - Set WORK_EMAIL to a valid inbox you own (e.g., a personal Gmail) that’s whitelisted for the iCloud relay, then retry the dry-run.\n- Option 2: Handshake-only with no send (test-only)\n  - Run the health check to verify login/NOOP only, no email send. This confirms credentials and relay reachability without hitting a recipient. We’ll log the handshake result and then you can re-run a dry-run once a whitelisted recipient is available.\n\nWhat I need from you\n- Choose Option 1 or 2.\n- If Option 1, provide a valid test recipient (email address). If you want, I can try using a known-good address you already have whitelisted.\n- If Option 2, I’ll run the handshake-only test and report the NOOP result.\n\nCurrent status recap\n- Credentials loaded: ICLOUD_EMAIL=dougyfresh_bot@icloud.com; ICLOUD_APP_PASSWORD updated.\n- Test recipient currently set to austin.king@parallon.com (causing 550 mailbox-not-found in this path).\n- I can switch to a different recipient you approve, or run a handshake-only test now. How would you like to proceed?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":203,"output":653,"cacheRead":83456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84312,"cost":{"input":-203,"output":-653,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-856}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772386023284}}
